description: Lexie's Frozen Custard is a delicious frozen treats truck serving the streets of the Bay Area. What is frozen custard? It’s the best soft serve ice cream you’ll ever have. It’s got a super smooth texture and is way more dense and creamy than other soft serve because there’s hardly any air incorporated in the freezing process. This custard is crazy popular in the Midwest, and now Lexie's is bringing that joy here to California!
name: Lexie's Frozen Custard
